Tab Manager lets you manage all tabs in one place. 

You can easily view, copy links and close the tabs from multiple windows. 

Tab manager provides below options:
[1] Copy URL's from all open tabs from multiple windows or current window.
[2] You can copy URL's and open them in multiple tabs.
